---
title: Sweet and Sticky Gochujang Halloumi Burger with Sesame Chips, Tomato and Rocket
description: A veggie favourite gets an upgrade in this Sweet and Sticky Gochujang Halloumi Burger. Sesame chips make the perfect side to a burger brimming with Korean inspired flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R05_W22_UK_V14507-3_Main_low-4a0456fe.jpg
